'''埃莉萨·隆戈·博尔吉尼'''（{{lang-it|Elisa Longo Borghini}}，{{bd|1991年|12月10日||}}）生于奥尔纳瓦索，是一名意大利女子自行车运动员，主攻公路自行车项目<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/lo/elisa-longo-borghini-1.html|title=Elisa Longo Borghini|work=Sport Reference|accessdate=2020-09-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180111165019/https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/lo/elisa-longo-borghini-1.html|archivedate=2018-01-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。她的父亲是一名前越野滑雪教练，母亲[[Guidina_Dal_Sasso|Guidina Dal Sasso]]是一名前[[越野滑雪|越野滑雪]]运动员，哥哥[[Paolo_Longo_Borghini|Paolo]]同样是一名自行车选手<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.famigliacristiana.it/articolo/longo-borghini-quando-lo-sport-e-di-famiglia.aspx|script-title=it:Longo Borghini: quando lo sport è di famiglia|publisher={{lang|it|Famiglia Cristiana}}|date=2012-09-26|accessdate=2020-09-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171018133541/http://www.famigliacristiana.it/articolo/longo-borghini-quando-lo-sport-e-di-famiglia.aspx|archivedate=2017-10-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=gazzetta>{{cite news |last=Bergonzi |first=Pier |title=World Championships: Vos wins Gold Longo Borghini claims Bronze |url=http://english.gazzetta.it/More_sports/22-09-2012/world-championships-vos-wins-gold-longo-borghini-claims-bronze--912685604027.shtml |newspaper=La Gazzetta dello Sport |date=2012-09-22 |author2=Scognamiglio, Ciro |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120925013235/http://english.gazzetta.it/More_sports/22-09-2012/world-championships-vos-wins-gold-longo-borghini-claims-bronze--912685604027.shtml |archivedate=2012-09-25 |accessdate=2020-09-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。她是意大利警察部队的一员，通过金色火焰（{{lang|it|Fiamme Oro}}）项目来维持自身的竞争力<ref>{{cite web|url=https://cyclingtips.com/2017/08/cycling-and-a-second-career-female-pro-cyclists-with-interesting-side-stories-part-1/|title=Cycling as a second career: a look at the other lives of cycling pros|work=Cycling Tips|date=2017-08-01|accessdate=2020-09-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170910220643/https://cyclingtips.com/2017/08/cycling-and-a-second-career-female-pro-cyclists-with-interesting-side-stories-part-1/|archivedate=2017-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

